sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?lake WHERE { ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?ol . ?ol geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . yago:Manchester geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER strdf:left(?geoWKT, ?geoWKT2) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT, ?geoWKT1) }

question: Which villages in Northumberland also border Alnwick?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?village WHERE { yago:Northumberland geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?ov . ?ov geo:asWKT ?geoWKTv . yago:Alnwick geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?geoWKTv, ?geoWKT1) FILTER geof:sfTouches(?geoWKTv, ?geoWKT2) }

question: Which parks are in Suffolk?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?park WHERE { yago:Suffolk geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?countyGeo . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?parkGeo FILTER geof:sfWithin(?parkGeo, ?countyGeo) }

question: Which forests in England are also east of Liverpool?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?forest WHERE { ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?ol . ?ol geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . yago:Liverpool geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER strdf:right(?geoWKT, ?geoWKT2) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT, ?geoWKT1) }

question: Which municipality in Attica is less than 50km away from Corinth?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?forest WHERE { <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Attica_(region)> geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?ov . ?ov geo:asWKT ?geoWKTv . yago:geoentity_Dimos_Corinth_8133673 geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?geoWKTv, ?geoWKT1) FILTER ( geof:distance(?geoWKTv, ?geoWKT2, uom:metre) < 50000 ) }

question: Which municipalities border with both Pallini and Agia Paraskevi?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?muni WHERE { ?muni rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?geom . ?geom geo:asWKT ?wkt . yago:Agia_Paraskevi geo:hasGeometry ?geom1 . ?geom1 geo:asWKT ?rpwkt . yago:Pallini geo:hasGeometry ?geom2 . ?geom2 geo:asWKT ?pwkt FILTER strdf:touches(?wkt, ?rpwkt) FILTER strdf:touches(?wkt, ?pwkt) }

question: Which municipalities contain at least one beach and one village?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?M WHERE { ?M rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?MGeo . ?MGeo geo:asWKT ?MPolygon . ?Forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?ForestGeo . ?ForestGeo geo:asWKT ?ForestPolygon . ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?xgeo . ?xgeo geo:asWKT ?xWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?ForestPolygon, ?MPolygon) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?xWKT, ?MPolygon) }

question: Give me 10 nature reserves that are west of townlands.
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?nr WHERE { ?nr rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_nature_reserve ; geo:hasGeometry ?nrGeo . ?nrGeo geo:asWKT ?nrWKt . ?townland rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Townland ; geo:hasGeometry ?TownlandGeo . ?TownlandGeo geo:asWKT ?TownlandWKt FILTER strdf:left(?nrWKt, ?TownlandWKt) } LIMIT 10

question: Which lakes border villages?
sparql: SELECT ?lake WHERE { ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?villageGeom . ?villageGeom geo:asWKT ?xWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?lakeGeom . ?lakeGeom geo:asWKT ?yWKT FILTER geof:sfTouches(?xWKT, ?yWKT) }

question: Which streams flow through cities?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?x WHERE { ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?cGeom1 . ?cGeom1 geo:asWKT ?cWKT1 . ?y rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_city ; geo:hasGeometry ?cGeom2 . ?cGeom2 geo:asWKT ?cWKT2 FILTER geof:sfCrosses(?cWKT1, ?cWKT2) }

question: Which forests are entirely within a barony and intersect with townlands?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?l WHERE { ?m rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Barony ; geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw . ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw . ?townland rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Townland ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg1 . ?lg1 geo:asWKT ?lw1 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?lw, ?lw1) }

question: Identify any nature reserves that are situated south of a forested area.
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?nature_reserve WHERE { ?nature_reserve rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_nature_reserve ; geo:hasGeometry ?nature_reserve_geo . ?nature_reserve_geo geo:asWKT ?nature_reserve_geoWKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?forest_geo . ?forest_geo geo:asWKT ?forest_geoWKT FILTER strdf:below(?nature_reserve_geoWKT, ?forest_geoWKT) }

question: Which towns have beaches?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?town WHERE { ?town rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_town ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoC . ?geoC geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoB . ?geoB geo:asWKT ?bWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?bWKT, ?cWKT) }

question: Which rural areas intersect with lakes?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?x WHERE { ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?xGeom . ?xGeom geo:asWKT ?xWKT . ?o rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Rural_Area ; geo:hasGeometry ?oGeom . ?oGeom geo:asWKT ?iWKT FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?xWKT, ?iWKT) }

question: What urban centers possess beaches?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?city WHERE { ?city rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_city ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoC . ?geoC geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoB . ?geoB geo:asWKT ?bWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?bWKT, ?cWKT) }

question: Which lakes are linked to a woodland area?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?x WHERE { ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?xGeom . ?xGeom geo:asWKT ?xWKT . ?o rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?oGeom . ?oGeom geo:asWKT ?iWKT FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?xWKT, ?iWKT) }

question: Which States of the US border with at most 2 other States?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?state WHERE { yago:United_States geo:hasGeometry ?usGeo . ?usGeo geo:asWKT ?usWKT . ?state rdf:type y2geoo:GADM_2ndOrder_AdministrativeUnit ; geo:hasGeometry ?sGeo . ?sGeo geo:asWKT ?sWKT . ?state2 rdf:type y2geoo:GADM_2ndOrder_AdministrativeUnit ; geo:hasGeometry ?s2Geo . ?s2Geo geo:asWKT ?s2WKT FILTER ( ( ( ( ?state != ?state2 ) && geof:sfWithin(?sWKT, ?usWKT) ) && geof:sfWithin(?s2WKT, ?usWKT) ) && geof:sfTouches(?sWKT, ?s2WKT) ) } GROUP BY ?state HAVING ( COUNT(?state2) <= 2 )

question: Is there a lake that touches both a forest and a village?
sparql: ASK WHERE { ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lGeo . ?lGeo geo:asWKT ?lWKT . ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?vGeo . ?vGeo geo:asWKT ?vWKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?fGeo . ?fGeo geo:asWKT ?fWKT FILTER ( geof:sfTouches(?vWKT, ?lWKT) && geof:sfTouches(?fWKT, ?lWKT) ) }

question: Give me a stream that crosses at least two lakes.
sparql: SELECT ?stream WHERE { ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?sGeo . ?sGeo geo:asWKT ?sWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lGeo . ?lGeo geo:asWKT ?lWKT FILTER geof:sfCrosses(?sWKT, ?lWKT) } GROUP BY ?stream HAVING ( COUNT(?lake) >= 3 ) LIMIT 1

question: Which localities are adjacent to lakes?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?locality WHERE { ?locality rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_locality ; geo:hasGeometry ?localityGeometry . ?localityGeometry geo:asWKT ?localityWKT . ?p rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?pGeometry . ?pGeometry geo:asWKT ?pWKT FILTER geof:sfTouches(?localityWKT, ?pWKT) }

question: Give me 5 streams that are on islands?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?river WHERE { ?island rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island ; geo:hasGeometry ?islandGeom . ?islandGeom geo:asWKT ?xWKT . ?river rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?riverGeom . ?riverGeom geo:asWKT ?yWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?yWKT, ?xWKT) } LIMIT 5

question: Which islands are situated within the boundaries of lakes?
sparql: SELECT ?village WHERE { ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island ; geo:hasGeometry ?villageGeom . ?villageGeom geo:asWKT ?xWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lakeGeom . ?lakeGeom geo:asWKT ?yWKT FILTER geof:sfContains(?yWKT, ?xWKT) }

question: How many Greek villages are either in a lake or in a forest?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?village) AS ?count) WHERE { { SELECT DISTINCT ?village WHERE { ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?vg . ?vg geo:asWKT ?vw . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?geo . ?geo geo:asWKT ?geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?vw, ?geoWKT) ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw FILTER geof:sfWithin(?vw, ?lw) } } UNION { SELECT DISTINCT ?village WHERE { ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?vg . ?vg geo:asWKT ?vw . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?geo . ?geo geo:asWKT ?geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?vw, ?geoWKT) ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?fg . ?fg geo:asWKT ?fw FILTER geof:sfWithin(?vw, ?fw) } } }

question: Which Irish Baronies contain both a lake and a forest?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?barony WHERE { ?barony rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Barony ; geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw . ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw . ?f rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?fg . ?fg geo:asWKT ?fw FILTER geof:sfWithin(?fw, ?mw) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) }

question: Which islands don't have any lakes but have forests?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?island WHERE { ?island rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island ; geo:hasGeometry ?iGeo . ?iGeo geo:asWKT ?iWKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?fGeo . ?fGeo geo:asWKT ?fWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?fWKT, ?iWKT) FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lGeo . ?lGeo geo:asWKT ?lWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?iWKT) } }

question: Which counties have no forests?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?county WHERE { { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_and_County_Council } ?county geo:hasGeometry ?countyGeom . ?countyGeom geo:asWKT ?countyWKT FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?fGeom . ?fGeom geo:asWKT ?fWKT FILTER geof:sfContains(?countyWKT, ?fWKT) } }

question: Which states do not contain any lakes?
sparql: SELECT ?state WHERE { yago:United_States geo:hasGeometry ?usGeo . ?usGeo geo:asWKT ?usWKT . ?state rdf:type y2geoo:GADM_2ndOrder_AdministrativeUnit ; geo:hasGeometry ?sGeo . ?sGeo geo:asWKT ?sWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?sWKT, ?usWKT) FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lGeo . ?lGeo geo:asWKT ?lWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?sWKT) } }

question: Which US state has no lakes?
sparql: SELECT ?state WHERE { yago:United_States geo:hasGeometry ?usGeo . ?usGeo geo:asWKT ?usWKT . ?state rdf:type y2geoo:GADM_2ndOrder_AdministrativeUnit ; geo:hasGeometry ?sGeo . ?sGeo geo:asWKT ?sWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?sWKT, ?usWKT) FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lGeo . ?lGeo geo:asWKT ?lWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?sWKT) } }

question: Are there any streams that cross villages in Central Greece?
sparql: ASK WHERE { <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Central_Greece_(region)> geo:hasGeometry ?geoC . ?geoC geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?vill rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoL . ?geoL geo:asWKT ?lWKT . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoS . ?geoS geo:asWKT ?sWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?cWKT) && geof:sfCrosses(?lWKT, ?sWKT) ) }

question: Which lakes intersect with forests in the Republic of Ireland?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?vill WHERE { yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?geoC . ?geoC geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?vill rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoL . ?geoL geo:asWKT ?lWKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoF . ?geoF geo:asWKT ?fWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?fWKT, ?cWKT) && geof:sfIntersects(?lWKT, ?fWKT) ) }

question: Which lakes in England intersect with streams?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?lake WHERE { yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?geoC . ?geoC geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoS . ?geoS geo:asWKT ?sWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoL . ?geoL geo:asWKT ?lWKT FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?sWKT, ?cWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?cWKT) ) && geof:sfIntersects(?lWKT, ?sWKT) ) }

question: Do beaches which are right next to lagoons that intersect with the municipality of Milos exist?
sparql: ASK WHERE { yago:geoentity_Dimos_Milos_8133681 geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?WKT . ?lagoon rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lagoon ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?WKT1 FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?WKT, ?WKT1) ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?WKT2 FILTER geof:sfTouches(?WKT2, ?WKT1) }

question: Which district wards share borders with civil parishes or communities that, in turn, border Oxford
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?city WHERE { yago:Oxford geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?WKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OS_CivilParishorCommunity ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?WKT1 . ?city rdf:type y2geoo:OS_DistrictWard ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?WKT2 FILTER geof:sfTouches(?WKT, ?WKT1) FILTER geof:sfTouches(?WKT2, ?WKT1) }

question: Which bays intersect with counties that border with County Mayo?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?bay WHERE { yago:County_Mayo geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?WKT { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_and_County_Council } ?county geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?WKT1 FILTER geof:sfTouches(?WKT, ?WKT1) ?bay rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_bay ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?WKT2 FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?WKT1, ?WKT2) }

question: Which Civil Parishes or Communites intersect Metropolitan District Wards in Birmingham?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?canal WHERE { yago:Birmingham geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?canal rdf:type y2geoo:OS_CivilParishorCommunity ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoPrk . ?geoPrk geo:asWKT ?canalWKT . ?town rdf:type y2geoo:OS_MetropolitanDistrictWard ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?townWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?townWKT, ?cWKT) && geof:sfIntersects(?townWKT, ?canalWKT) ) }

question: Which bays are east of parks in Dublin?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?bay WHERE { yago:Dublin geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoPrk . ?geoPrk geo:asWKT ?parkWKT . ?bay rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_bay ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?bayWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?parkWKT, ?cWKT) && strdf:right(?bayWKT, ?parkWKT) ) }

question: Which beaches intersect villages on Corfu Island?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?beach WHERE { yago:Corfu geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?beaWKT . ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoVillage . ?geoVillage geo:asWKT ?vilWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?vilWKT, ?cWKT) && geof:sfIntersects(?vilWKT, ?beaWKT) ) }

question: Which streams cross municipalities that are located in the region of Thessaly?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?stream WHERE { yago:Thessaly geo:hasGeometry ?lgeo . ?lgeo geo:asWKT ?lWKT . ?county rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?geo . ?geo geo:asWKT ?WKT . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?sgeo . ?sgeo geo:asWKT ?sWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?WKT, ?lWKT) FILTER geof:sfCrosses(?WKT, ?sWKT) }

question: Which streams cross counties that border Cumbria ?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?stream WHERE { yago:Cumbria geo:hasGeometry ?lgeo . ?lgeo geo:asWKT ?lWKT . ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?geo . ?geo geo:asWKT ?WKT . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?sgeo . ?sgeo geo:asWKT ?sWKT FILTER geof:sfTouches(?lWKT, ?WKT) FILTER geof:sfCrosses(?WKT, ?sWKT) }

question: Which streams cross counties that border County Longford?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?stream WHERE { yago:County_Longford geo:hasGeometry ?lgeo . ?lgeo geo:asWKT ?lWKT { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_and_County_Council } ?county geo:hasGeometry ?geo . ?geo geo:asWKT ?WKT . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?sgeo . ?sgeo geo:asWKT ?sWKT FILTER geof:sfTouches(?lWKT, ?WKT) FILTER geof:sfCrosses(?WKT, ?sWKT) }

question: Which bays are east of a reservoir in Greece?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?bay WHERE { yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?rep1 . ?rep1 geo:asWKT ?WKT1 . ?reservoir rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_reservoir ; geo:hasGeometry ?rep2 . ?rep2 geo:asWKT ?WKT2 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?WKT2, ?WKT1) ?bay rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_bay ; geo:hasGeometry ?rep3 . ?rep3 geo:asWKT ?WKT3 FILTER strdf:right(?WKT3, ?WKT2) }

question: Which streams intersect Unitary Authority Wards in Edinburgh?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?stream WHERE { yago:Edinburgh geo:hasGeometry ?rep1 . ?rep1 geo:asWKT ?WKT1 . ?UnitaryAuthorityWard rdf:type y2geoo:OS_UnitaryAuthorityWard ; geo:hasGeometry ?rep2 . ?rep2 geo:asWKT ?WKT2 FILTER geof:sfContains(?WKT1, ?WKT2) ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?rep3 . ?rep3 geo:asWKT ?WKT3 FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?WKT2, ?WKT3) }

question: Which localities are in towns that intersect with County Roscommon?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?locality WHERE { yago:County_Roscommon geo:hasGeometry ?rep1 . ?rep1 geo:asWKT ?WKT1 . ?town rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_town ; geo:hasGeometry ?rep2 . ?rep2 geo:asWKT ?WKT2 FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?WKT2, ?WKT1) ?locality rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_locality ; geo:hasGeometry ?rep3 . ?rep3 geo:asWKT ?WKT3 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?WKT3, ?WKT2) }

question: Which districts of Suffolk have forests within them?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?district WHERE { yago:Suffolk geo:hasGeometry ?Suffolk_geo . ?Suffolk_geo geo:asWKT ?Suffolk_geoWKT . ?district rdf:type y2geoo:OS_District ; geo:hasGeometry ?district_geo . ?district_geo geo:asWKT ?district_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?district_geoWKT, ?Suffolk_geoWKT) ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?forest_geo . ?forest_geo geo:asWKT ?forest_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?forest_geoWKT, ?district_geoWKT) }

question: Which Irish counties that border County Kildare intersect with canals?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?county WHERE { yago:County_Kildare geo:hasGeometry ?kildare_geo . ?kildare_geo geo:asWKT ?kildare_geoWKT . ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council ; geo:hasGeometry ?county_geo . ?county_geo geo:asWKT ?county_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfTouches(?county_geoWKT, ?kildare_geoWKT) ?canal rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_canal ; geo:hasGeometry ?canal_geo . ?canal_geo geo:asWKT ?canal_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?canal_geoWKT, ?county_geoWKT) }

question: Which lakes are within counties in England?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?lake WHERE { ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT, ?geoWKT1) yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?oen . ?oen geo:asWKT ?geoWKToen FILTER geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT, ?geoWKToen) }

question: Which forests intersect with rural areas in the Republic of Ireland?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?forest WHERE { ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Rural_Area ; geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?i . ?i geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT, ?geoWKT2) }

question: Which municipalities intersect with parks in the Central Athens regional unit.
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?m WHERE { ?m rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?om . ?om geo:asWKT ?geoWKTm . yago:geoentity_Perifereiakí_Enótita_Kentrikoú_Toméa_Athinón_8200482 geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomP . ?geomP geo:asWKT ?geoWKTP FILTER geof:sfWithin(?geoWKTm, ?geoWKT1) FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?geoWKTP, ?geoWKTm) }

question: Which county bordering the city of Cork contains the largest lake?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?county (strdf:area(?B) AS ?biggest_lake) WHERE { yago:geoentity_Cork_City_7778678 geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?A { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_and_County_Council } ?county geo:hasGeometry ?geomC . ?geomC geo:asWKT ?C . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomB . ?geomB geo:asWKT ?B FILTER geof:sfTouches(?C, ?A) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?B, ?C) } ORDER BY DESC(?biggest_lake) LIMIT 1

question: Are there district wards within districts in Cambridge?
sparql: ASK WHERE { y2geor:Geometry_gadm_GBR.1.16_1 geo:asWKT ?C . ?District rdf:type y2geoo:OS_District ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?A . ?DistrictWard rdf:type y2geoo:OS_DistrictWard ; geo:hasGeometry ?geom . ?geom geo:asWKT ?B FILTER geof:sfWithin(?B, ?A) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?A, ?C) }

question: Which regional unit in the region of Epirus has a lake?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?city WHERE { <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Epirus_(region)> geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?A . ?city rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_RegionalUnit ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomC . ?geomC geo:asWKT ?C . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomB . ?geomB geo:asWKT ?B FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?B, ?A) && geof:sfWithin(?B, ?C) ) }

question: Is there a lagoon located north of a beach in Thasos?
sparql: ASK WHERE { yago:Thasos geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?xWKT2 . ?x2 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?x2Geom . ?x2Geom geo:asWKT ?iWKT2 . ?x1 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lagoon ; geo:hasGeometry ?x1Geom . ?x1Geom geo:asWKT ?iWKT1 FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?iWKT1, ?xWKT2) && geof:sfWithin(?iWKT2, ?xWKT2) ) && strdf:above(?iWKT1, ?iWKT2) ) }

question: Give me exactly one park of Dublin that is south of a canal.
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?x2 WHERE { yago:Dublin geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?xWKT2 . ?x2 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?x2Geom . ?x2Geom geo:asWKT ?iWKT2 . ?x1 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_canal ; geo:hasGeometry ?x1Geom . ?x1Geom geo:asWKT ?iWKT1 FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?iWKT2, ?xWKT2) && strdf:below(?iWKT2, ?iWKT1) ) } LIMIT 1

question: Which villages in Birmingham are north of canals?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?village WHERE { yago:Birmingham geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?prkWKT . ?canal rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_canal ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoPrk . ?geoPrk geo:asWKT ?lWKT . ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?cWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?prkWKT) && strdf:above(?cWKT, ?lWKT) ) }

question: Which islands are south of beaches in Naxos?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?island WHERE { yago:Naxos geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?lcnWKT . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?lWKT . ?island rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoIsl . ?geoIsl geo:asWKT ?IslWKT FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?lcnWKT) && strdf:below(?IslWKT, ?lWKT) ) && ( ?island != yago:Naxos ) ) }

question: Are there any bays next to parks in Dublin?
sparql: ASK WHERE { yago:Dublin geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?prkWKT . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoPrk . ?geoPrk geo:asWKT ?lWKT . ?bay rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_bay ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?cWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?prkWKT) && geof:sfTouches(?cWKT, ?lWKT) ) }

question: Which beaches are located on the islands of Greece?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?lake WHERE { ?island rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island ; geo:hasGeometry ?ig . ?ig geo:asWKT ?igeoWKT . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?g2 . ?g2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT FILTER strdf:within(?igeoWKT, ?geoWKT) ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lgeoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lgeoWKT, ?igeoWKT) }

question: Which Irish city councils have parks?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?x WHERE { ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_Council ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?irlG . ?irlG geo:asWKT ?irlWKT . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?lcnWKT . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?lWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?irlWKT) && geof:sfContains(?lcnWKT, ?lWKT) ) }

question: Which are the unitary authorities of England that border with Scotland?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?d WHERE { ?d rdf:type y2geoo:OS_UnitaryAuthority ; geo:hasGeometry ?cGeom . ?cGeom geo:asWKT ?cWKT . yago:Scotland geo:hasGeometry ?geom . ?geom geo:asWKT ?iWKT . yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?geom1 . ?geom1 geo:asWKT ?iWKT1 FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?cWKT, ?iWKT1) && geof:sfTouches(?cWKT, ?iWKT) ) }

question: Is there a lake inside a forest in County Wicklow?
sparql: ASK WHERE { ?x1 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?x1Geo . ?x1Geo geo:asWKT ?x1WKT . ?x2 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?x2Geo . ?x2Geo geo:asWKT ?x2WKT . yago:County_Wicklow geo:hasGeometry ?x3Geo . ?x3Geo geo:asWKT ?x3WKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?x1WKT, ?x3WKT) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?x1WKT, ?x2WKT) }

question: Which municipalities have lakes in Central Macedonia?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?municipality WHERE { ?municipality rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?g1 . ?g1 geo:asWKT ?wkt1 . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?g2 . ?g2 geo:asWKT ?wkt2 . yago:Central_Macedonia geo:hasGeometry ?g3 . ?g3 geo:asWKT ?wkt3 FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?wkt2, ?wkt3) && geof:sfContains(?wkt1, ?wkt2) ) }

question: Is there a village that is next to a nature reserve in England?
sparql: ASK WHERE { ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?g1 . ?g1 geo:asWKT ?wkt1 . ?nature_reserve rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_nature_reserve ; geo:hasGeometry ?g2 . ?g2 geo:asWKT ?wkt2 . yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?g3 . ?g3 geo:asWKT ?wkt3 FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?wkt2, ?wkt3) && geof:sfTouches(?wkt1, ?wkt2) ) }

question: Which streams in the Republic of Ireland are tributaries?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?river WHERE { ?river rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?g1 . ?g1 geo:asWKT ?wkt1 . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?g2 . ?g2 geo:asWKT ?wkt2 . yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?g3 . ?g3 geo:asWKT ?wkt3 FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?wkt2, ?wkt3) && geof:sfIntersects(?wkt1, ?wkt2) ) && geof:sfCrosses(?wkt1, ?wkt2) ) }

question: Which forests are within baronies in the Republic of Ireland?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?for WHERE { ?for rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?forestGeo . ?barony rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Barony ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?baronyGeo . yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?ir . ?ir geo:asWKT ?irWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?forestGeo, ?baronyGeo) && geof:sfWithin(?baronyGeo, ?irWKT) ) }

question: Which Greek municipalities have beaches?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?municipality WHERE { ?municipality rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?munWKT . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?beachWKT . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?grgeo . ?grgeo geo:asWKT ?grWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?beachWKT, ?munWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?munWKT, ?grWKT) ) }

question: Which parks are inside counties of England?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?park WHERE { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?countyGeo . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?parkGeo . yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?englGeo FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?countyGeo, ?englGeo) && geof:sfWithin(?parkGeo, ?countyGeo) ) }

question: Which towns have lakes in the Kilmacrenan barony?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?town WHERE { yago:geoentity_Kilmacrenan_2963284 geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?baronyWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?lakeWKT . ?town rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Townland ; geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?townWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?townWKT, ?baronyWKT) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lakeWKT, ?townWKT) }

question: Which municipalities south of Kastoria have a lake?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?municipality WHERE { yago:Kastoria geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?kastoriaWKT . ?municipality rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?munWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?lakeWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lakeWKT, ?munWKT) FILTER strdf:below(?munWKT, ?kastoriaWKT) }

question: Which localities are south of lakes in County Cavan?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?locality WHERE { yago:County_Cavan geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?locality rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_locality ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT3 FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT1) && geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT3, ?geoWKT1) ) && strdf:below(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT3) ) }

question: In Breckland district, which forests are south of streams?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?forest WHERE { yago:Breckland_District geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT3 FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT1) && geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT3, ?geoWKT1) ) && strdf:below(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT3) ) }

question: Which villages are north of beaches, in Thessaly?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?village WHERE { yago:Thessaly geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT3 FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT1) && geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT3, ?geoWKT1) ) && strdf:above(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT3) ) }

question: Which districts that are located south of Staffordshire have forests?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?district WHERE { yago:Staffordshire geo:hasGeometry ?Staffordshire_geo . ?Staffordshire_geo geo:asWKT ?Staffordshire_geoWKT . ?district rdf:type y2geoo:OS_District ; geo:hasGeometry ?district_geo . ?district_geo geo:asWKT ?district_geoWKT FILTER strdf:below(?district_geoWKT, ?Staffordshire_geoWKT) ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?forest_geo . ?forest_geo geo:asWKT ?forest_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?forest_geoWKT, ?district_geoWKT) }

question: Which rural areas located south of County Longford have forests?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?Rural_Area WHERE { yago:County_Longford geo:hasGeometry ?Longford_geo . ?Longford_geo geo:asWKT ?Longford_geoWKT . ?Rural_Area rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Rural_Area ; geo:hasGeometry ?Rural_Area_geo . ?Rural_Area_geo geo:asWKT ?Rural_Area_geoWKT FILTER strdf:below(?Rural_Area_geoWKT, ?Longford_geoWKT) ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?forest_geo . ?forest_geo geo:asWKT ?forest_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?forest_geoWKT, ?Rural_Area_geoWKT) }

question: Which rural areas are located on the northern side of the city of Cork and have forests?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?Rural_Area WHERE { yago:geoentity_Cork_City_7778678 geo:hasGeometry ?Longford_geo . ?Longford_geo geo:asWKT ?Longford_geoWKT . ?Rural_Area rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Rural_Area ; geo:hasGeometry ?Rural_Area_geo . ?Rural_Area_geo geo:asWKT ?Rural_Area_geoWKT FILTER strdf:above(?Rural_Area_geoWKT, ?Longford_geoWKT) ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?forest_geo . ?forest_geo geo:asWKT ?forest_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?forest_geoWKT, ?Rural_Area_geoWKT) }

question: Which forests contain streams in the State of Iowa?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?forest WHERE { yago:Iowa geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT) ) && geof:sfContains(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT2) ) }

question: Which villages are north of lakes, in County Cumbria?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?village WHERE { yago:Cumbria geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT) ) && strdf:above(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT2) ) }

question: Which villages are located east of beaches, in Corfu?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?village WHERE { yago:Corfu geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT) ) && strdf:right(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT2) ) }

question: Which lakes are entirely contained by a Greek municipality?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?l WHERE { ?m rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw . ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?grgeo . ?grgeo geo:asWKT ?grWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?mw, ?grWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) ) }

question: Which forests are entirely within an English County?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?l WHERE { ?m rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw . ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw . yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?englGeo FILTER geof:sfWithin(?mw, ?englGeo) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) }

question: Which forests are entirely within an Irish Barony?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?l WHERE { yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?irlG . ?irlG geo:asWKT ?irlWKT . ?m rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Barony ; geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw . ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?mw, ?irlWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) ) }

question: Which forests are entirely contained in counties that are west of the county of Norfolk?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?l WHERE { yago:Norfolk geo:hasGeometry ?ng . ?ng geo:asWKT ?nw . ?m rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw FILTER strdf:right(?nw, ?mw) ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) }

question: Which forests are entirely contained in baronies east of Coshlea?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?l WHERE { y2geor:osientity_2AE19629112213A3E055000000000001 geo:hasGeometry ?ng . ?ng geo:asWKT ?nw . ?m rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Barony ; geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw FILTER strdf:left(?nw, ?mw) ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) }

question: Which districts of Cambridge have forests?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?district WHERE { ?district rdf:type y2geoo:OS_District ; geo:hasGeometry ?districtGeo . ?districtGeo geo:asWKT ?districtWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?lakeGeo . ?lakeGeo geo:asWKT ?lakeWKT . yago:Cambridge geo:hasGeometry ?x2Geo . ?x2Geo geo:asWKT ?x2WKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?districtWKT, ?x2WKT) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lakeWKT, ?districtWKT) }

question: Which civil parishes in Ireland contain more than 10 townlands?
sparql: SELECT ?civilParish WHERE { ?civilParish rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Civil_Parish . ?townland rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Townland ; geo:sfWithin ?civilParish } GROUP BY ?civilParish HAVING ( COUNT(?townland) > 10 )

question: Which greek municipalities have more than 5 beaches?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?mun (COUNT(?beach) AS ?beaches) WHERE { { SELECT DISTINCT ?mun ?beach WHERE { ?mun rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?a . ?a geo:asWKT ?A . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?b . ?b geo:asWKT ?B FILTER strdf:contains(?A, ?B) } } } GROUP BY ?mun HAVING ( ?beaches > 5 )

question: Which streams cross lakes in Scotland?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?p1 WHERE { ?p1 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?p1geo . ?p1geo geo:asWKT ?p1WKT . ?p2 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?p2geo . ?p2geo geo:asWKT ?p2WKT . yago:Scotland geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?sWKT FILTER ( geof:sfCrosses(?p1WKT, ?p2WKT) && geof:sfWithin(?p2WKT, ?sWKT) ) }

question: Which nature reserves in Ireland have lakes within their boundaries?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?p1 WHERE { ?p1 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_nature_reserve ; geo:hasGeometry ?p1geo . ?p1geo geo:asWKT ?p1WKT . ?p2 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?p2geo . ?p2geo geo:asWKT ?p2WKT . yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?iWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?p1WKT, ?iWKT) && geof:sfContains(?p1WKT, ?p2WKT) ) }

question: Which villages are located on islands in South Aegean
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?p1 WHERE { ?p1 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?p1geo . ?p1geo geo:asWKT ?p1WKT . ?p2 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island ; geo:hasGeometry ?p2geo . ?p2geo geo:asWKT ?p2WKT . yago:South_Aegean geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?gWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?p2WKT, ?gWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?p1WKT, ?p2WKT) ) }

question: Which forests intersect with villages in the State of Illinois?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?forest WHERE { ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?vg . ?vg geo:asWKT ?vgeoWKT . yago:Illinois geo:hasGeometry ?g2 . ?g2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT FILTER strdf:within(?vgeoWKT, ?geoWKT) ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?fg . ?fg geo:asWKT ?fgeoWKT FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?vgeoWKT, ?fgeoWKT) }

question: Which parks are located within the boundaries of cities in Orange County, California
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?park WHERE { ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?pg . ?pg geo:asWKT ?pgeoWKT . ?city rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_city ; geo:hasGeometry ?cg . ?cg geo:asWKT ?cgeoWKT . <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Orange_County,_California> geo:hasGeometry ?g . ?g geo:asWKT ?geoWKT FILTER ( strdf:within(?cgeoWKT, ?geoWKT) && strdf:within(?pgeoWKT, ?cgeoWKT) ) }

question: Which islands are east of villages in Greece?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?x WHERE { ?y rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?ygeo . ?ygeo geo:asWKT ?yWKT . ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island ; geo:hasGeometry ?xgeo . ?xgeo geo:asWKT ?xWKT . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?grgeo . ?grgeo geo:asWKT ?grWKT FILTER ( ( geof:sfContains(?grWKT, ?xWKT) && geof:sfContains(?grWKT, ?yWKT) ) && strdf:right(?xWKT, ?yWKT) ) }

question: Which canals are located to the north of forests in England?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?y WHERE { ?y rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_canal ; geo:hasGeometry ?ygeo . ?ygeo geo:asWKT ?yWKT . ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?xgeo . ?xgeo geo:asWKT ?xWKT . yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?ukgeo . ?ukgeo geo:asWKT ?ukWKT FILTER ( ( geof:sfContains(?ukWKT, ?xWKT) && geof:sfContains(?ukWKT, ?yWKT) ) && strdf:below(?xWKT, ?yWKT) ) }

question: Which lakes in Ireland are adjacent to forests?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?y WHERE { ?y rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?ygeo . ?ygeo geo:asWKT ?yWKT . ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?xgeo . ?xgeo geo:asWKT ?xWKT . yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?irgeo . ?irgeo geo:asWKT ?irWKT FILTER ( ( geof:sfContains(?irWKT, ?xWKT) && geof:sfContains(?irWKT, ?yWKT) ) && geof:sfTouches(?yWKT, ?xWKT) ) }

question: Which municipalities of Attica have at least one beach?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?Municip WHERE { ?Municip geo:sfWithin <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Attica_(region)> . ?Municp rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?MunicpGeo . ?MunicpGeo geo:asWKT ?MunicpPolygon . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?beachGeo . ?beachGeo geo:asWKT ?beachPolygon FILTER geof:sfWithin(?beachPolygon, ?MunicpPolygon) }

question: Which parks in the US engulf at least one lake inside them?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?prk WHERE { yago:United_States geo:hasGeometry ?USGeo . ?USGeo geo:asWKT ?USPolygon . ?prk rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?prkGeo . ?prkGeo geo:asWKT ?prkPolygon . ?lk rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lkGeo . ?lkGeo geo:asWKT ?lkPolygon FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?prkPolygon, ?USPolygon) && geof:sfWithin(?lkPolygon, ?USPolygon) ) && geof:sfContains(?prkPolygon, ?lkPolygon) ) }

question: Can you provide me with the names of 4 villages located in rural areas south of Dublin?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?vil WHERE { yago:Dublin geo:hasGeometry ?dblnGeo . ?dblnGeo geo:asWKT ?dblnPolygon . ?vil rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?vilGeo . ?vilGeo geo:asWKT ?vilPolygon . ?ra rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Rural_Area ; geo:hasGeometry ?raGeo . ?raGeo geo:asWKT ?raPolygon FILTER ( strdf:below(?raPolygon, ?dblnPolygon) && geof:sfWithin(?vilPolygon, ?raPolygon) ) } LIMIT 4

question: Is there a park north of a stream in Attica?
sparql: ASK WHERE { ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?parkGeometry . ?parkGeometry geo:asWKT ?parkWKT . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?streamGeometry . ?streamGeometry geo:asWKT ?streamWKT . <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Attica_(region)> geo:hasGeometry ?attikiGeo . ?attikiGeo geo:asWKT ?attikiWKT FILTER ( ( strdf:above(?parkWKT, ?streamWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?parkWKT, ?attikiWKT) ) && geof:sfWithin(?streamWKT, ?attikiWKT) ) }

question: Which lakes are north of a canal in London?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?a WHERE { ?a rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?g1 . ?b rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_canal ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?g2 . yago:Greater_London geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?g3 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?g1, ?g3) FILTER geof:sfCrosses(?g2, ?g3) FILTER strdf:above(?g2, ?g1) }

question: Which localities are located east of forests in County Wicklow?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?a WHERE { yago:County_Wicklow geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?a rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_locality ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?b rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT) ) && strdf:right(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT2) ) }

question: Which reservoirs are located within third-order administrative units in Greece?

question: Which reservoirs are east of 3rd order administrative units in Ireland?

question: Which streams cross a town in England?

question: Which streams cross nature reserves in the United Kingdom?

sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?river WHERE { ?river rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?g1 . ?g1 geo:asWKT ?wkt1 . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?g2 . ?g2 geo:asWKT ?wkt2 . yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?g3 . ?g3 geo:asWKT ?wkt3 FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?wkt2, ?wkt3) && geof:sfIntersects(?wkt1, ?wkt2) ) && geof:sfCrosses(?wkt1, ?wkt2) ) }

question: Are there lakes located inside forests in Ireland?
sparql: ASK WHERE { ?for rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?forestGeo . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?lakeGeo . yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?ir . ?ir geo:asWKT ?irWKT FILTER ( geof:sfContains(?forestGeo, ?lakeGeo) && geof:sfWithin(?lakeGeo, ?irWKT) ) }

question: Which municipalities in Greece have parks?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?municipality WHERE { ?municipality rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?munWKT . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?beachWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?beachWKT, ?munWKT) }

question: Which county of Great Britain has the most lakes?
sparql: SELECT ?county (COUNT(?park) AS ?parkCount) WHERE { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?countyWKT . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?parkWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?parkWKT, ?countyWKT) } GROUP BY ?county ORDER BY DESC(?parkCount) LIMIT 1

question: Which villages are south of beaches in Peloponnese?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?village WHERE { <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Peloponnese_(region)> geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER ( ( strdf:within(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT) && strdf:within(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT) ) && strdf:below(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT2) ) }

question: Which lakes are entirely contained by a Greek region?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?l WHERE { ?m rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Region ; geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw . ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?mw, ?geoWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) ) }

question: Which lakes are entirely within an Irish Barony?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?l WHERE { yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?irlG . ?irlG geo:asWKT ?irlWKT . ?m rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Barony ; geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw . ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?mw, ?irlWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) ) }

question: Are there forests that are entirely contained in a region which is south of Corfu?
sparql: ASK WHERE { ?m rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Region . yago:Corfu geo:hasGeometry ?cg . ?m geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?cg geo:asWKT ?cw . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw FILTER strdf:below(?mw, ?cw) ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) }

question: Which parks are entirely contained in counties that are east of the county of Longford?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?l WHERE { yago:County_Longford geo:hasGeometry ?ng . ?ng geo:asWKT ?nw . ?m rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw FILTER strdf:left(?nw, ?mw) ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) }

question: Which lakes are entirely contained in baronies west of Coshlea?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?l WHERE { y2geor:osientity_2AE19629112213A3E055000000000001 geo:hasGeometry ?ng . ?ng geo:asWKT ?nw . ?m rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Barony ; geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw FILTER strdf:right(?nw, ?mw) ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) }

question: Can you determine the names of the lakes in Greece that are completely encompassed within a single municipality?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?l WHERE { ?m rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw . ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) }

question: What are the parks situated in the forests of the United States?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?p1 WHERE { ?p1 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?p1geo . ?p1geo geo:asWKT ?p1WKT . ?p2 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?p2geo . ?p2geo geo:asWKT ?p2WKT . yago:United_States geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?gWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?p2WKT, ?gWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?p1WKT, ?p2WKT) ) }

question: Can you identify the woodland areas in the districts situated to the south of Staffordshire?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?district WHERE { yago:Staffordshire geo:hasGeometry ?Staffordshire_geo . ?Staffordshire_geo geo:asWKT ?Staffordshire_geoWKT . ?district rdf:type y2geoo:OS_District ; geo:hasGeometry ?district_geo . ?district_geo geo:asWKT ?district_geoWKT FILTER strdf:below(?district_geoWKT, ?Staffordshire_geoWKT) ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?forest_geo . ?forest_geo geo:asWKT ?forest_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?forest_geoWKT, ?district_geoWKT) }

question: What are the lakes intersecting a flowing body of water in Oregon?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?lake WHERE { ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lakeGeometry . ?lakeGeometry geo:asWKT ?lakeWKT . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?streamGeometry . ?streamGeometry geo:asWKT ?streamWKT . yago:Oregon geo:hasGeometry ?oregonGeo . ?oregonGeo geo:asWKT ?oregonWKT FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?lakeWKT, ?oregonWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?streamWKT, ?oregonWKT) ) && geof:sfIntersects(?lakeWKT, ?streamWKT) ) }

question: What are the parks situated on islands of the US?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?p1 WHERE { ?p1 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?p1geo . ?p1geo geo:asWKT ?p1WKT . ?p2 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island ; geo:hasGeometry ?p2geo . ?p2geo geo:asWKT ?p2WKT . yago:United_States geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?gWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?p2WKT, ?gWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?p1WKT, ?p2WKT) ) }

question: Which county in Wales has the smallest number of villages?
sparql: SELECT ?county WHERE { SELECT ?county (COUNT(?village) AS ?villages) WHERE { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?cGeom . ?cGeom geo:asWKT ?cWKT . yago:Wales geo:hasGeometry ?wGeom . ?wGeom geo:asWKT ?wWKT . ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?villageGeom . ?villageGeom geo:asWKT ?xWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?cWKT, ?wWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?xWKT, ?cWKT) ) } GROUP BY ?county } ORDER BY ?villages LIMIT 1

question: Which regional units of Greece share a border with three regional units?
sparql: SELECT ?municipalUnit WHERE { ?municipalUnit rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_RegionalUnit ; geo:hasGeometry ?muGeo . ?muGeo geo:asWKT ?muWKT . ?municipalUnit2 rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_RegionalUnit ; geo:hasGeometry ?mu2Geo . ?mu2Geo geo:asWKT ?mu2WKT FILTER ( ( ?municipalUnit != ?municipalUnit2 ) && geof:sfTouches(?muWKT, ?mu2WKT) ) } GROUP BY ?municipalUnit HAVING ( COUNT(?municipalUnit2) = 3 )

question: Is there a lake that intersects with all the regional units of Epirus?
sparql: ASK WHERE { { SELECT ?lake WHERE { ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lakeGeo . ?lakeGeo geo:asWKT ?lakeWKT . ?region rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_RegionalUnit ; geo:hasGeometry ?regionGeo . ?regionGeo geo:asWKT ?regionWKT . <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Epirus_(region)> geo:hasGeometry ?eGeo . ?eGeo geo:asWKT ?eWKT FILTER ( geof:sfContains(?eWKT, ?regionWKT) && geof:sfIntersects(?lakeWKT, ?regionWKT) ) } GROUP BY ?lake HAVING ( COUNT(?region) = 4 ) } }

question: Which US states border with Arkansas?
sparql: SELECT ?state WHERE { yago:United_States geo:hasGeometry ?usGeo . ?usGeo geo:asWKT ?usWKT . yago:Arkansas geo:hasGeometry ?cGeo . ?cGeo geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?state rdf:type y2geoo:GADM_2ndOrder_AdministrativeUnit ; geo:hasGeometry ?sGeo . ?sGeo geo:asWKT ?sWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?sWKT, ?usWKT) && geof:sfTouches(?sWKT, ?cWKT) ) }

question: Which US counties intersect with Missouri?
sparql: SELECT ?county WHERE { yago:United_States geo:hasGeometry ?usGeo . ?usGeo geo:asWKT ?usWKT . yago:Missouri geo:hasGeometry ?cGeo . ?cGeo geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?county rdf:type y2geoo:GADM_3rdOrder_AdministrativeUnit ; geo:hasGeometry ?ctGeo . ?ctGeo geo:asWKT ?ctWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?ctWKT, ?usWKT) && geof:sfIntersects(?ctWKT, ?cWKT) ) }

question: Which lake in Northern Ireland intersects with the most counties?
sparql: SELECT ?lake WHERE { { SELECT ?lake ?county WHERE { yago:Northern_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?niGeo . ?niGeo geo:asWKT ?niWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lGeo . ?lGeo geo:asWKT ?lWKT . ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?cGeo . ?cGeo geo:asWKT ?cWKT FILTER ( ( geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?niWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?cWKT, ?niWKT) ) && geof:sfIntersects(?lWKT, ?cWKT) ) } } } GROUP BY ?lake ?county ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?county)) LIMIT 1

question: Which US states border with Texas?
sparql: SELECT ?state WHERE { yago:United_States geo:hasGeometry ?usGeo . ?usGeo geo:asWKT ?usWKT . yago:Texas geo:hasGeometry ?mGeo . ?mGeo geo:asWKT ?mWKT . ?state rdf:type y2geoo:GADM_2ndOrder_AdministrativeUnit ; geo:hasGeometry ?sGeo . ?sGeo geo:asWKT ?sWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?sWKT, ?usWKT) && geof:sfTouches(?sWKT, ?mWKT) ) }

question: Which town of Ireland is closest to Northern Ireland?
sparql: SELECT ?town (geof:distance(?tWKT, ?niWKT, uom:metre) AS ?dist) WHERE { yago:Northern_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?niGeo . ?niGeo geo:asWKT ?niWKT . ?town rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_town ; geo:hasGeometry ?tGeo . ?tGeo geo:asWKT ?tWKT . yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?iGeo . ?iGeo geo:asWKT ?iWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?tWKT, ?iWKT) } ORDER BY ?dist LIMIT 1

question: Which lakes are entirely contained in a Greek municipality which is east of Chania?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?l WHERE { ?m rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality . geo:geoentity_Chania_8133762 geo:hasGeometry ?cg . ?m geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?cg geo:asWKT ?cw . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?mg, ?geoWKT) && strdf:right(?mw, ?cw) ) ?l rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw) }

question: Which townlands are south of streams and baronies in the county of Longford?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?forest WHERE { yago:County_Longford geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Townland ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Barony ; geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT3 FILTER ( ( ( ( geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT) ) && geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT3, ?geoWKT) ) && strdf:below(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT2) ) && strdf:below(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT3) ) }

question: Which villages are north of lakes and parks in County Cumbria?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?village WHERE { yago:Cumbria geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT3 FILTER ( ( ( ( geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT) ) && geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT3, ?geoWKT) ) && strdf:above(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT2) ) && strdf:above(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT3) ) }

question: Which English counties have both forests and lakes?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?island WHERE { yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?gGeo . ?gGeo geo:asWKT ?gWKT . ?island rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?iGeo . ?iGeo geo:asWKT ?iWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?iWKT, ?gWKT) ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?fGeo . ?fGeo geo:asWKT ?fWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?fWKT, ?iWKT) ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lGeo . ?lGeo geo:asWKT ?lWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?iWKT) }

question: Which Greek regions have no lakes?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?region WHERE { ?region rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Region ; geo:hasGeometry ?regionGeom . ?regionGeom geo:asWKT ?regionWKT . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?regionWKT, ?geoWKT) FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lGeom . ?lGeom geo:asWKT ?lWKT FILTER strdf:contains(?regionWKT, ?lWKT) } }

question: Which Greek municipalities do not have any parks?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?mun WHERE { ?mun rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?munGeom . ?munGeom geo:asWKT ?munWKT . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?munWKT, ?geoWKT) FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?pGeom . ?pGeom geo:asWKT ?pWKT FILTER strdf:contains(?munWKT, ?pWKT) } }

question: Which Irish counties have no forestlands?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?county WHERE { { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_and_County_Council } ?county geo:hasGeometry ?countyGeom . ?countyGeom geo:asWKT ?countyWKT FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?fGeom . ?fGeom geo:asWKT ?fWKT FILTER strdf:contains(?countyWKT, ?fWKT) } }

question: How big is the park in Essex?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT (strdf:area(?parkGeo) AS ?parkArea) WHERE { yago:Essex geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?countyGeo . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?parkGeo FILTER geof:sfWithin(?parkGeo, ?countyGeo) }

question: Which municipalities that belong to Periferiaki Enotita Nison and have less than 3000 residents individually, contain islands?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?dimos WHERE { yago:geoentity_Perifereiakí_Enótita_Níson_8200487 geo:hasGeometry ?aGeo . ?aGeo geo:asWKT ?A . ?dimos geo:hasGeometry ?dimos_geo . ?dimos_geo geo:asWKT ?dimos_geoWKT . ?dimos y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?dimos_pop FILTER ( ?dimos_pop < 3000 ) ?island rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island ; geo:hasGeometry ?island_geo . ?island_geo geo:asWKT ?island_geoWKT FILTER ( geof:sfWithin(?dimos_geoWKT, ?A) && geof:sfIntersects(?island_geoWKT, ?dimos_geoWKT) ) }

question: What is the name and the area of the parks that are in Wards of Northern Ireland that are east of Dublin?
sparql: SELECT ?locality ?parkArea WHERE { { SELECT ?locality (strdf:area(?locality_geoWKT) AS ?parkArea) ?locality_geoWKT ?geoWKT WHERE { yago:Dublin geo:hasGeometry ?city_geometry . ?city_geometry geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?ward rdf:type y2geoo:OSNI_Ward ; geo:hasGeometry ?ward_geo . ?ward_geo geo:asWKT ?ward_geoWKT . ?locality rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?locality_geo . ?locality_geo geo:asWKT ?locality_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?locality_geoWKT, ?ward_geoWKT) } } FILTER strdf:right(?locality_geoWKT, ?geoWKT) }

question: Which municipalities in Central Macedonia have a population of more than 50.000 people?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?municipality WHERE { ?municipality rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?population ; geo:hasGeometry ?om . ?om geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . yago:Central_Macedonia geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT, ?geoWKT1) FILTER ( ?population > 50000 ) }

question: Give me the population of islands located in Greece.
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?pop ?x WHERE { ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island ; geo:hasGeometry ?xGeom ; y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?pop . ?xGeom geo:asWKT ?xWKT . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?iWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?xWKT, ?iWKT) }

question: Is the area of any canal that intersects with Dublin greater than zero?
sparql: ASK WHERE { ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_canal ; geo:hasGeometry ?xGeom . ?xGeom geo:asWKT ?xWKT . yago:Dublin geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?iWKT FILTER ( geof:sfIntersects(?xWKT, ?iWKT) && ( strdf:area(?xWKT) > 0 ) ) }

question: Which municipalities in Greece have a population of less than 30000?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?x WHERE { ?x rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?xgeo . ?xgeo geo:asWKT ?xWKT . ?x y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?pop . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?grgeo . ?grgeo geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?xWKT, ?geoWKT1) FILTER ( ?pop < 30000 ) }

question: Which regional units of the Peloponnese have more than 30.000 inhabitants?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?x1 WHERE { ?x1 rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_RegionalUnit . <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Peloponnese_(region)> geo:hasGeometry ?aGeo . ?aGeo geo:asWKT ?A . ?x1 y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?p ; geo:hasGeometry ?x1Geo . ?x1Geo geo:asWKT ?x1WKT FILTER ( ?p > 30000 ) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?x1WKT, ?A) }

question: Which local government districts in Northern Ireland, north of Belfast, have an area of more than 1000000 square meters?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?x1 WHERE { ?x1 rdf:type y2geoo:OSNI_LocalGovermentDistrict ; y2geoo:hasOSNI_Area ?area ; geo:hasGeometry ?x1Geo . ?x1Geo geo:asWKT ?x1WKT . yago:geoentity_City_of_Belfast_3333223 geo:hasGeometry ?x2Geo . ?x2Geo geo:asWKT ?x2WKT FILTER strdf:above(?x1WKT, ?x2WKT) FILTER ( ?area > 1000000 ) }

question: What is the area of each forest in the Scarawalsh Barony?
sparql: SELECT ?forest (strdf:area(?forestWKT) AS ?forestArea) WHERE { yago:geoentity_Scarawalsh_Bridge_3304299 geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?baronyWKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?forestWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?forestWKT, ?baronyWKT) }

question: What is the population of the municipalities that border Kastoria?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?municipality ?population WHERE { yago:Kastoria geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?kastoriaWKT . ?municipality rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?munWKT . ?municipality y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?population FILTER geof:sfTouches(?kastoriaWKT, ?munWKT) }

question: Which municipality in Crete has a population over 20000?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?m WHERE { yago:Crete geo:hasGeometry ?g . ?g geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?m rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mgeoWKT FILTER strdf:within(?mgeoWKT, ?geoWKT) ?m y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?p FILTER ( ?p > 20000 ) }

question: Is there a village in Scotland with an area smaller than 0.05 square kilometers?
sparql: ASK WHERE { ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?vg . ?vg geo:asWKT ?vgeoWKT . yago:Scotland geo:hasGeometry ?g . ?g geo:asWKT ?geoWKT FILTER strdf:within(?vgeoWKT, ?geoWKT) FILTER ( strdf:area(?vgeoWKT) < 0.05 ) }

question: Which towns in County Longford with area bigger than 0.01 are west of Dublin?
sparql: SELECT ?town WHERE { ?town rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_town ; geo:hasGeometry ?tg . ?tg geo:asWKT ?tgeoWKT . yago:County_Longford geo:hasGeometry ?g . ?g geo:asWKT ?geoWKT FILTER strdf:within(?tgeoWKT, ?geoWKT) FILTER ( strdf:area(?tgeoWKT) > 0.01 ) yago:Dublin geo:hasGeometry ?dg . ?dg geo:asWKT ?dgeoWKT FILTER strdf:left(?geoWKT, ?dgeoWKT) }

question: Which Greek regional units have less than 10000 inhabitants?
sparql: SELECT ?region WHERE { ?region rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_RegionalUnit ; y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?pop FILTER ( ?pop < 10000 ) }

question: Which municipalities in the Central Athens Regional Unit have less than 50000 residents and contain parks?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?dimos WHERE { yago:geoentity_Perifereiakí_Enótita_Kentrikoú_Toméa_Athinón_8200482 geo:hasGeometry ?mgeo . ?mgeo geo:asWKT ?mWKT . ?dimos geo:hasGeometry ?dimos_geo . ?dimos_geo geo:asWKT ?dimos_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfContains(?mWKT, ?dimos_geoWKT) ?dimos y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?dimos_pop FILTER ( ?dimos_pop < 50000 ) ?island rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park . ?park geo:hasGeometry ?park_geo . ?park_geo geo:asWKT ?parkWKT FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?parkWKT, ?dimos_geoWKT) }

question: What are the names of the lakes in the Northern Irish wards west of Wales?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?locality WHERE { yago:Wales geo:hasGeometry ?city_geometry . ?city_geometry geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?ward rdf:type y2geoo:OSNI_Ward ; geo:hasGeometry ?ward_geo . ?ward_geo geo:asWKT ?ward_geoWKT FILTER strdf:left(?ward_geoWKT, ?geoWKT) ?locality rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?locality_geo . ?locality_geo geo:asWKT ?locality_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?locality_geoWKT, ?ward_geoWKT) }

question: What are the largest lakes that belong to counties south of Epping Forest?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?locality (strdf:area(?locality_geoWKT) AS ?lakeArea) WHERE { yago:Epping_Forest geo:hasGeometry ?for_geo . ?for_geo geo:asWKT ?for_geoWKT . ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?county_geo . ?county_geo geo:asWKT ?county_geoWKT FILTER strdf:above(?for_geoWKT, ?county_geoWKT) ?locality rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?locality_geo . ?locality_geo geo:asWKT ?locality_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?locality_geoWKT, ?county_geoWKT) } ORDER BY DESC(?lakeArea) LIMIT 1

question: Which municipalities in Central Athens that intersect with a park have a population of more than 10.000 people?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?municipality WHERE { ?municipality rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?population ; geo:hasGeometry ?om . ?om geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . yago:geoentity_Perifereiakí_Enótita_Kentrikoú_Toméa_Athinón_8200482 geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?parkGeometry . ?parkGeometry geo:asWKT ?parkWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT, ?geoWKT1) FILTER strdf:intersects(?geoWKT, ?parkWKT) FILTER ( ?population > 10000 ) }

question: Which is the number of inhabitants residing on the islands situated within Greece?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?pop ?x WHERE { ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island ; geo:hasGeometry ?xGeom ; y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?pop . ?xGeom geo:asWKT ?xWKT . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?iWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?xWKT, ?iWKT) }

question: Which Greek regions have between 500000 and 1000000 inhabitants?
sparql: SELECT ?region WHERE { ?region rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Region ; geo:hasGeometry ?regionGeom . ?regionGeom geo:asWKT ?xWKT . ?region y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?pop . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?iWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?xWKT, ?iWKT) FILTER ( ?pop < 1000000 ) FILTER ( ?pop > 500000 ) }

question: Which states only have counties with 1000 inhabitants or more?
sparql: SELECT ?state WHERE { ?state rdf:type yago:wikicategory_States_of_the_United_States ; geo:hasGeometry ?stateGeom . ?stateGeom geo:asWKT ?stateWKT FILTER NOT EXISTS { ?county y2geoo:hasGADM_Description "County" ; geo:hasGeometry ?cGeom . ?cGeom geo:asWKT ?cWKT FILTER geof:sfContains(?stateWKT, ?cWKT) ?county y2geoo:POPULATION ?pop BIND(xsd:double(?pop) AS ?popd) FILTER ( ?popd < 1000 ) } }

question: How many lakes are there in Los Angeles?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?lake) AS ?lakes) WHERE { yago:geoentity_Los_Angeles_City_Center_6946540 geo:hasGeometry ?laGeom . ?laGeom geo:asWKT ?laWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lakeGeom . ?lakeGeom geo:asWKT ?lakeWKT FILTER geof:sfContains(?laWKT, ?lakeWKT) }

question: Find the number of forests in England.
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?x) AS ?forests) WHERE { yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?lcnWKT . ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?lWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?lcnWKT) }

question: What is the total number of localities in County Roscommon, and what is their total and average area?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?locality) AS ?total) (SUM(strdf:area(?WKT2)) AS ?sum) (AVG(strdf:area(?WKT2)) AS ?avg) WHERE { yago:County_Roscommon geo:hasGeometry ?rep1 . ?rep1 geo:asWKT ?WKT1 . ?locality rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_locality ; geo:hasGeometry ?rep2 . ?rep2 geo:asWKT ?WKT2 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?WKT2, ?WKT1) }

question: What is the average number of beaches located in the municipalities to the west of Pyrgos in the Elis region?
sparql: SELECT ?reg_unit (AVG(?no_of_beaches) AS ?avg_no_of_beaches) WHERE { <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Pyrgos,_Elis> geo:hasGeometry ?pirgos_geo . ?pirgos_geo geo:asWKT ?pirgos_geoWKT . ?reg_unit rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?reg_unitgeo . ?reg_unitgeo geo:asWKT ?reg_unitgeoWKT FILTER strdf:left(?reg_unitgeoWKT, ?pirgos_geoWKT) ?locality rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?locality_geo . ?locality_geo geo:asWKT ?locality_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?locality_geoWKT, ?reg_unitgeoWKT) } GROUP BY ?reg_unit

question: What is the total number of lakes and the total number of streams located within the city limits of Cork?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?lake) AS ?total_lakes) (COUNT(DISTINCT ?stream) AS ?total_streams) WHERE { yago:geoentity_Cork_City_7778678 geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?A . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomB . ?geomB geo:asWKT ?B . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomC . ?geomC geo:asWKT ?C FILTER geof:sfWithin(?B, ?A) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?C, ?A) }

question: How many parks and how many streams are there in Essex?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?park) AS ?total_parks) (COUNT(DISTINCT ?stream) AS ?total_streams) WHERE { yago:Essex geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?A . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomB . ?geomB geo:asWKT ?B . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomC . ?geomC geo:asWKT ?C FILTER geof:sfWithin(?B, ?A) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?C, ?A) }

question: How many lakes does Greece have?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(?x) AS ?cnt) WHERE { ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?xGeom . ?xGeom geo:asWKT ?xWKT . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?iWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?xWKT, ?iWKT) }

question: How many lakes are there in England?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?x) AS ?lakes) WHERE { yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?lcnWKT . ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?lWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?lcnWKT) }

question: How many parks does Dublin have and what is their total area?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(?park) AS ?count) (SUM(strdf:area(?lWKT)) AS ?total_area_of_parks) WHERE { yago:Dublin geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?lcnWKT . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?lWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?lcnWKT) }

question: What is the total area of lakes in Monaghan?
sparql: SELECT (SUM(?lakeArea) AS ?oSum) WHERE { { SELECT (strdf:area(?lakeWKT) AS ?lakeArea) WHERE { y2geor:osientity_2AE1962941E413A3E055000000000001 geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?baronyWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?lakeWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lakeWKT, ?baronyWKT) } } }

question: What is the number of lakes in each county that has lakes?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?county (COUNT(?lake) AS ?lake_count) WHERE { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC . ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?lcWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?lWKT FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?lWKT, ?lcWKT) } GROUP BY ?county

question: What is the maximum area among lakes located in County Cavan?
sparql: SELECT DISTINCT (MAX(strdf:area(?geoWKT2)) AS ?maxLakeArea) WHERE { yago:County_Cavan geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT1) }

question: What are the smallest, largest and average forest areas that are within a district which is placed south of Staffordshire?
sparql: SELECT (MIN(strdf:area(?forest_geoWKT)) AS ?areas_min) (MAX(strdf:area(?forest_geoWKT)) AS ?areas_max) (AVG(strdf:area(?forest_geoWKT)) AS ?areas_avg) WHERE { yago:Staffordshire geo:hasGeometry ?Suffolk_geo . ?Suffolk_geo geo:asWKT ?Suffolk_geoWKT . ?district rdf:type y2geoo:OS_District ; geo:hasGeometry ?district_geo . ?district_geo geo:asWKT ?district_geoWKT FILTER strdf:below(?district_geoWKT, ?Suffolk_geoWKT) ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?forest_geo . ?forest_geo geo:asWKT ?forest_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?forest_geoWKT, ?district_geoWKT) }

question: What is the average area of the forests that are within the Rural Area south of Cork City?
sparql: SELECT (AVG(?areas) AS ?areas_avg) WHERE { SELECT (strdf:area(?forest_geoWKT) AS ?areas) WHERE { yago:geoentity_Cork_City_7778678 geo:hasGeometry ?Cork_geo . ?Cork_geo geo:asWKT ?Cork_geoWKT . ?rural_area rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Rural_Area ; geo:hasGeometry ?rural_area_geo . ?rural_area_geo geo:asWKT ?rural_area_geoWKT FILTER strdf:above(?rural_area_geoWKT, ?Cork_geoWKT) ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?forest_geo . ?forest_geo geo:asWKT ?forest_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?forest_geoWKT, ?rural_area_geoWKT) } }

question: How many lakeside villages are there?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?village) AS ?villages) WHERE { ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoV . ?geoV geo:asWKT ?vWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoL . ?geoL geo:asWKT ?lWKT FILTER geof:sfTouches(?lWKT, ?vWKT, uom:metre) }

question: How many streams cross forests?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?stream) AS ?streams) WHERE { ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoF . ?geoF geo:asWKT ?fWKT . ?stream rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_stream ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoS . ?geoS geo:asWKT ?sWKT FILTER geof:sfCrosses(?sWKT, ?fWKT) }

question: How many cities have beaches?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?city) AS ?cities) WHERE { ?city rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_city ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoC . ?geoC geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?geoB . ?geoB geo:asWKT ?bWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?bWKT, ?cWKT) }

question: How many islands are within a Greek region?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?island) AS ?islands) WHERE { ?region rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Region ; geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?WKT . ?island rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?WKT1 . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?iWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?WKT, ?iWKT) FILTER geof:sfWithin(?WKT1, ?WKT) }

question: How many English districts contain parks?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?district) AS ?districts) WHERE { ?district rdf:type y2geoo:OS_District ; geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?WKT . ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?WKT1 . yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?egeo . ?egeo geo:asWKT ?eWKT FILTER ( geof:sfContains(?WKT, ?WKT1) && geof:sfContains(?eWKT, ?WKT) ) }

question: How many townlands intersect with lakes?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?townland) AS ?townlands) WHERE { ?townland rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Townland ; geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?WKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?WKT1 FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?WKT, ?WKT1) }

question: What is the number of forests that are right next to a lake?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?forest) AS ?forests) WHERE { ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?x1Geo . ?x1Geo geo:asWKT ?x1WKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?x2Geo . ?x2Geo geo:asWKT ?x2WKT FILTER geof:sfTouches(?x1WKT, ?x2WKT) }

question: How many parks are located within city limits?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?park) AS ?parks) WHERE { ?park rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_park ; geo:hasGeometry ?x1Geo . ?x1Geo geo:asWKT ?x1WKT . ?city rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_city ; geo:hasGeometry ?x2Geo . ?x2Geo geo:asWKT ?x2WKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?x1WKT, ?x2WKT) }

question: What is the number of bays that are adjacent to villages?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?bay) AS ?bays) WHERE { ?bay rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_bay ; geo:hasGeometry ?x1Geo . ?x1Geo geo:asWKT ?x1WKT . ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?x2Geo . ?x2Geo geo:asWKT ?x2WKT FILTER geof:sfTouches(?x1WKT, ?x2WKT) }

question: How many municipalities contain at least one lake?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?mun) AS ?municipalities) WHERE { ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?vgeo . ?vgeo geo:asWKT ?vWKT . ?mun rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality ; geo:hasGeometry ?mgeo . ?mgeo geo:asWKT ?mWKT FILTER geof:sfContains(?mWKT, ?vWKT) }

question: How many counties contain at least one reservoir?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?county) AS ?counties) WHERE { ?res rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_reservoir ; geo:hasGeometry ?vgeo . ?vgeo geo:asWKT ?vWKT { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_and_County_Council } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County } ?county geo:hasGeometry ?mgeo . ?mgeo geo:asWKT ?mWKT FILTER geof:sfContains(?mWKT, ?vWKT) }

question: How many counties have beaches?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?county) AS ?counties) WHERE { { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_and_County_Council } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County } ?county geo:hasGeometry ?cgeo . ?cgeo geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?bgeo . ?bgeo geo:asWKT ?bWKT FILTER geof:sfContains(?cWKT, ?bWKT) }

question: How many greek regions have a beach?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?region) AS ?regions) WHERE { ?region rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Region ; geo:hasGeometry ?rep1 . ?rep1 geo:asWKT ?WRT1 . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?rep2 . ?rep2 geo:asWKT ?WRT2 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?WRT2, ?WRT1) }

question: What is the number of Counties that intersect with lakes?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?county) AS ?counties) WHERE { { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_and_County_Council } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County } ?county geo:hasGeometry ?geomc . ?geomc geo:asWKT ?WKT1 . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomf . ?geomf geo:asWKT ?WKT2 FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?WKT2, ?WKT1) }

question: What is the total number of baronies which have nature reserves?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?x) AS ?baronies) WHERE { ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Barony ; geo:hasGeometry ?cGeom1 . ?cGeom1 geo:asWKT ?cWKT1 . ?y rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_nature_reserve ; geo:hasGeometry ?cGeom2 . ?cGeom2 geo:asWKT ?cWKT2 FILTER geof:sfWithin(?cWKT2, ?cWKT1) }

question: How many nature reserves intersect with forests?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?nature_reserve) AS ?nature_reserves) WHERE { ?nature_reserve rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_nature_reserve ; geo:hasGeometry ?nature_reserve_geo . ?nature_reserve_geo geo:asWKT ?nature_reserve_geoWKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?forest_geo . ?forest_geo geo:asWKT ?forest_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?forest_geoWKT, ?nature_reserve_geoWKT) }

question: How many administrative level 3 entities have oxbows?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?order3adm) AS ?adms) WHERE { ?order3adm y2geoo:hasGADM_NationalLevel "3rdOrder" ; geo:hasGeometry ?order3adm_geo . ?order3adm_geo geo:asWKT ?order3adm_geoWKT . ?oxbow rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_oxbow ; geo:hasGeometry ?oxbow_geo . ?oxbow_geo geo:asWKT ?oxbow_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?oxbow_geoWKT, ?order3adm_geoWKT) }

question: What is the number of islands that have lakes?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?island) AS ?islands) WHERE { ?island rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island ; geo:hasGeometry ?island_geo . ?island_geo geo:asWKT ?island_geoWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?lake_geo . ?lake_geo geo:asWKT ?lake_geoWKT FILTER geof:sfWithin(?lake_geoWKT, ?island_geoWKT) }

question: How many nature reserves intersect with towns?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?natureReserve) AS ?natureReserves) WHERE { ?town rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_town ; geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?natureReserve rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_nature_reserve ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?geoWKT, ?geoWKT1) }

question: How many villages border towns?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?village) AS ?villages) WHERE { ?town rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_town ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER geof:sfTouches(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT2) }

question: How many beaches are next to cities?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?beach) AS ?beaches) WHERE { ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach ; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?city rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_city ; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 FILTER geof:sfTouches(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT2) }

question: How many district wards are within districts?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?DistrictWard) AS ?wards) WHERE { ?District rdf:type y2geoo:OS_District ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?A . ?DistrictWard rdf:type y2geoo:OS_DistrictWard ; geo:hasGeometry ?geom . ?geom geo:asWKT ?B FILTER geof:sfWithin(?B, ?A) }

question: How many lakes are within Irish counties?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?lake) AS ?lakes) WHERE { ?CountyCouncil rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council ; geo:hasGeometry ?geomL . ?geomL geo:asWKT ?A . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?geom . ?geom geo:asWKT ?B FILTER geof:sfWithin(?B, ?A) }

question: What is the number of lakes that are connected to a forest?
sparql: SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?x) AS ?lakes) WHERE { ?x rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake ; geo:hasGeometry ?xGeom . ?xGeom geo:asWKT ?xWKT . ?o rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest ; geo:hasGeometry ?oGeom . ?oGeom geo:asWKT ?iWKT FILTER geof:sfIntersects(?xWKT, ?iWKT) }

question: How many baronies border with city councils?
